name: Turning Point.
description:
Is a new curated style, been drawing things since 2014 and now i’ve found what style that really fit to me. 

The artwork also depict a long run journey, and it speaks to the art style discoveries during the years.

from psychedelic, abstract, geometric, also an optical art for my newest discoveries. 

Hopefully, it could represent the larger truth in my art journey.

Thanks.
